{"operationName":"poolsList","variables":{"first":100,"orderBy":"createdAt","orderDirection":"desc","skip":0,"where":{"isClosed":false}},"query":"query poolsList($first: Int = 100, $orderBy: Pool_orderBy = createdAt, $orderDirection: OrderDirection = desc, $skip: Int = 0, $where: Pool_filter) {
  pools(
    first: $first
    orderBy: $orderBy
    orderDirection: $orderDirection
    skip: $skip
    where: $where
  ) {
    ...PoolFragment
    __typename
  }
}

fragment PoolFragment on Pool {
  id
  name
  access
  stableCoin
  owner
  members
  joins
  minDeposit
  totalDeposited
  totalBorrowed
  createdAt
  isClosed
  rewardApy
  assetsLocked {
    ...AssetFragment
    __typename
  }
  members
  __typename
}

fragment AssetFragment on Asset {
  id
  hash
  uri
  value
  riskRating
  maturityDate
  owner
  isLocked
  isRedeemed
  uploadedAt
  __typename
}
"}
